snippet.textDisplay: Pakistan Coke Studio is incredible. The women singing in their local language is soulful. I don’t understand Sindhi so subtitles helped me to understand the lines. The video is just another level. Local clothes are so beautiful with such mixture of colours. Pakistan Coke Studio has such deep sense of music and representing the different cultures in Pakistan. Synchronisation of so many tools. Overall, it’s just amazing and so thoughtful.
